{"tid":1392015,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[源頭減廢]電子化免費垃圾報，和理非既你一定要推!","createTime":"2019-07-31T15:15:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T11:15:21.000Z","uid":43114,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2869eebc9e57876f46681d0934a0ce3c8f525e7d","tid":1392015,"uid":43114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:15:40.000Z","msg":"眾所周知，過量用紙係環保既死敵<br />\n每份大公報都損耗緊地球既樹木<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n為響應環保，小弟提議兩階段的行動<br />\n<br />\n第一階段:<br />\n印電子新聞媒體既QR CODE 廣泛貼係派發點既附近<br />\n第二階段: <br />\nConnect環保團體向免費報章作出呼籲，要求減印及轉為電子化<br />\n<br />\n最終目標係源頭減廢取代免費報，順手幫讀者轉返個合適既媒體閱讀<strong>中立既報導</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n常見免費派既<del>垃圾</del>報紙:<br />\nAm730 <br />\n晴報<br />\n頭條日報<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大公報<br />\n文匯報</span><br />\n<br />\n第一階段:<br />\n希望各位由自己屋苑同路經既MTR站入手，要比18區所有街坊都意識到環保既重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟拋個磚:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aaTH1SL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaaTH1SL.png&h=0bbe0b8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好似唔夠位放其他報紙，唯有等5大訴求回應左再更新啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一階段好處係成本低又有光環，但缺點係難有報社/物業管理處支持<br />\n<br />\n第二階段:<br />\n出信SEND EMAIL Connect環保團體+環境保護署，由佢地出面先係最有力既呼籲<br />\n長春社, 環保觸覺, 香港地球之友 ,  綠色和平, 環境保護署etc<br />\n少左樹多左CO2又影響全球暖化，少左廢紙海龜都長命D<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n減少廢紙爭議一定比膠飲管低，要長期抗爭各種文宣一定要做好!<br />\n<br />\n小弟文筆唔好，又唔係環保專長<br />\n希望有其他巴絲幫幫忙整理圖片或文章<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位加油!"},{"pid":"356ebdbdba22939bdd21a3926e4f7543f16bb2c6","tid":1392015,"uid":25899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:16:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6341bff0cb24b4ed1936f32082124ee636cb8da3","tid":1392015,"uid":392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:21:44.000Z","msg":"見到有大公報唔該一人拎一份去回收/墊枱/執狗屎/dum撚左佢"},{"pid":"f3c7a9bc231826921891c6ffe846c2b0f54d45c2","tid":1392015,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:29:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f146c832bf57e53ce6ea3273248202486437e0d4","tid":1392015,"uid":43114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T16:45:42.000Z","msg":"！"},{"pid":"f5a0d486580a04e6b4c7ae8088875751a79cd04e","tid":1392015,"uid":198309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:04:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d762dd4b9f13b0a3342caced9a3fe59cef49044a","tid":1392015,"uid":33500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:29:25.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"5e9178ced7bfdf274b429bc4443558fffa5ebd12","tid":1392015,"uid":43114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:54:27.000Z","msg":"！！！"},{"pid":"1434ccacd94ff2c9fa0624f64e396fac9a36cf40","tid":1392015,"uid":187634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:56:04.000Z","msg":"值得支持"},{"pid":"4dcd9a80530bf8e2f9fb27ed5516144ddc55ef5e","tid":1392015,"uid":43114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1434ccacd94ff2c9fa0624f64e396fac9a36cf40","tid":1392015,"uid":187634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:56:04.000Z","msg":"值得支持"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:31:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f87968eb796e3b4bcebe132ed911de4c1e2bea05","tid":1392015,"uid":43114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:16:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c29275b1aaf818b8354fa64f3dafc0a6dc7bf816","tid":1392015,"uid